Dragons for Peadir:
	If Peadir rolls high enough, Kikka, the kobold info broker of Pildrylth, will approach Peadir with information on the different dragons in the
	area. His real goal is to get Peadir to alter the ballance of power and give Pildrylth an opportunity to gain more control.
